      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; boundary conditions in simulation match nominal experimental setup.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment of simulation input parameters to experimental conditions is not required at MRL 2. Inlet flow rate and outlet pressure boundary conditions are set to match nominal experimental operating points. Any residual differences are captured within the output comparison uncertainty budget."
